				<h4><a href="http://whay.me/piano-teaching/e-newsletter/creatures-great-and-small-student-concert-series">&#8220;Creatures Great and Small&#8221; Student Concert Series</a></h4>				
				<div class="postMeta bullet cat-item-90">
					Posted on 29/05/2012					by <a href="http://whay.me/author/Will">Will Hay</a>
					<span></span>									</div>

				<div class="postBody">
					<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://gfl.whay.me"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2322" title="The Geoffles Daily" src="http://whay.me/wp-content/uploads/header2.jpg" alt="" width="448" height="165" /></a>The banner above links to &#8220;<a title="The Geoffles Daily" href="http://gfl.whay.me" target="_blank">The Geoffles Daily</a>&#8220;, a daily photoblog of my kitten Geoffrey following his antics since he came to live with us on April 13th. The daily photos from the photoblog automatically syndicate to a <a title="The Geoffles Daily on Facebook" href="http://facebook.com/thegeofflesdaily" target="_blank">facebook</a> page and an <a title="The Geoffles Daily on Evernote" href="http://whay.me/gflden" target="_blank">evernote </a>folder!</p>
<p><img class="alignright  wp-image-2325" style="margin: 5px;" title="Concert Invite" src="http://whay.me/wp-content/uploads/180612concert-199x300.jpg" alt="" width="159" height="240" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Appropriately, the concert series this term will follow an animal theme with the title &#8220;Creatures Great and Small&#8221;. The school concerts will showcase the talents of my piano pupils within each school with a range of solos, duets and own compositions and each will culminate with this term&#8217;s multimedia collaboration project in which a number of students have taken part along with members of the <a title="Chester Music Society Youth Choir" href="http://cmsyc.org.uk" target="_blank">Chester Music Society Youth Choir</a>.</p>
<p>Parents of the children involved are cordially invited to attend the concert in schools and everybody is invited to the final concert in the series taking place at All Saint&#8217;s which will again be supporting a Kampala Music School piano bursary with audience tickets priced at £3/adult and £1/child.</p>
<p><strong>St. Oswald&#8217;s, Mollington &#8211; Friday 15th June at 9:15am</strong></p>
<p><strong>St. Werburgh&#8217;s Primary &#8211; Monday 18th June at 9:10am</strong></p>
<p><strong>Saighton School &#8211; Friday 22nd June at 9:10am</strong></p>
<p><strong>Upton Heath Primary &#8211; Monday 25th June at 9am</strong></p>
<p><strong>All Saint&#8217;s Church &#8211; Saturday 30th June at 11am</strong></p>
<p>A <a title="Spring Concerts 2012" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8ga6nVa4298" target="_blank">concert preview video</a> below features excerpts from the Spring Concert Series earlier this year.</p>
<hr />
<p style="text-align: center;"><object width="450" height="337" classid="clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000" codebase="http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0"><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><param name="src" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/8ga6nVa4298?version=3&amp;hl=en_US&amp;rel=0" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><embed width="450" height="337" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" src="http://www.youtube.com/v/8ga6nVa4298?version=3&amp;hl=en_US&amp;rel=0" allowFullScreen="true" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true" /></object></p>
