				<h4><a href="http://whay.me/weddings/love-songs-for-a-summer-ceremony">Love songs for a Summer Ceremony</a></h4>				
				<div class="postMeta bullet cat-item-68">
					Posted on 14/05/2012					by <a href="http://whay.me/author/Will">Will Hay</a>
					<span></span>									</div>

				<div class="postBody">
					<p><img class="alignleft  wp-image-2236" style="margin: 5px;" title="Wedding outside in the &quot;Temple&quot; at Willington Hall" src="http://whay.me/wp-content/uploads/weddings-300x189.jpg" alt="" width="216" height="136" />Having just returned from playing outdoors at a super ceremony and reception at <a href="http://www.willingtonhall.co.uk/special-events/weddings/">Willington Hall</a>, I thought I would share some inspiration for music choices at your summer wedding ceremony.</p>
<p><strong>Music before the ceremony</strong>:<br />
People sometimes like to specify a type of music they would like to be played while the guests are taking their seats, perhaps including one or two songs with some special meaning.<br />
<iframe src="http://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F42975022&amp;auto_play=false&amp;show_artwork=true&amp;color=ff8b09" frameborder="no" scrolling="no" width="100%" height="166"></iframe><br />
Adele- Make you feel my love, Bryan Adams &#8211; Everything I do, Glasgow Love Theme from Love Actually, Eric Clapton &#8211; Wonderful Tonight, Aerosmith &#8211; I don&#8217;t want to miss a thing</p>
<p><strong>Music for the Arrival of the Bride:<br />
</strong><iframe src="http://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F43086021&amp;auto_play=false&amp;show_artwork=true&amp;color=ff8b09" frameborder="no" scrolling="no" width="100%" height="166"></iframe>Alicia Keys &#8211; If I ain&#8217;t got you, Lou Reed &#8211; Perfect Day, Lionel Richie &#8211; Say you, say me, Leona Lewis &#8211; A moment like this</p>
<p><strong>Signing of the register:</strong><br />
<iframe src="http://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F46329345&amp;show_artwork=true" frameborder="no" scrolling="no" width="100%" height="166"></iframe><br />
Eva Cassidy &#8211; Songbird, Beatles &#8211; All you need is love, Elvis Costello &#8211; She, Ben E King &#8211; Stand by Me</p>
<p><strong>Music for the exit of the couple:</strong><br />
<iframe src="http://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F46331270&amp;show_artwork=true" frameborder="no" scrolling="no" width="100%" height="166"></iframe><br />
Norah Jones &#8211; Come away with me, Katie Melua &#8211; Closest thing to crazy, Stevie Wonder &#8211; Isn&#8217;t she lovely?, Pachelbel &#8211; Canon in D</p>
<p>Dates are still available for bookings in 2012/13. <a title="Contact" href="http://whay.me/contact">Contact me for availability</a></p>
<h5>We can&#8217;t always rely on the weather but we can help you to select some songs to set the mood for your special day!</h5>
